9 COMMITTEE SUBSTITUTE
10 An Act relating to schools; amending 70 O.S. 2021,
Section 27-103, which relates to requirements for
11 school athletic association written policies; adding
requirement that certain hearings be subject to
12 certain act; repealing 70 O.S. 2021, Section 8-103.2,
which relates to participation in certain
13 competitions after certain transfer; providing an
effective date; and declaring an emergency.
14
15
16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 27-103, is
18 amended to read as follows:
19 Section 27-103. A public school or school district shall not be
20 a member of any school athletic association unless that association
21 has adopted a written policy that requires the following:
22 1. All records of the association to be made accessible
23 consistent with the provisions of the Oklahoma Open Records Act;
24
Req. No. 3945 Page 1

1 2. All meetings of the association to be open and conducted in
2 a manner consistent with the provisions of the Oklahoma Open Meeting
3 Act, including specifically the notice and agenda, voting, and
4 executive session requirements. All hearings of the association
5 including, but not limited to, hearings for rule violations,
6 eligibility determinations, and requests for hardship waivers shall
7 be subject to the Oklahoma Open Meeting Act; and
8 3. An annual financial audit and a compliance audit of all
9 funds of the association in accordance with the auditing standards
10 set forth in the Oklahoma Public School Audit Law. In addition, the
11 association shall have performance audits conducted of the
12 operations of the association. A performance audit shall be
13 conducted no later than December 31, 2014, and by December 31 every
14 five (5) years thereafter.
15 SECTION 2. REPEALER 70 O.S. 2021, Section 8-103.2, is
16 hereby repealed.
17 SECTION 3. This act shall become effective July 1, 2026.
18 SECTION 4. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
19 of the public peace, health, or safety, an emergency is hereby
20 declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
21 be in full force from and after its passage and approval.
